#SURGEDEAMON

this deamon is a super low level embedded software client(deamon) for the surge smart home operating system!
This is designed and programmed by Randall Perkins!

This is a personal project of mine, that i'm building for my personal smart home system.
I'll post updates to my personal twitter @thetmrgate when i can, if you have questions.
please feel free to message me on there!

###Supported Platforms 
- Ubuntu
- Raspberry Pi
- Freebsd (To come in the future)
- Windows 10 (To come in the future)


###Deps
- clang
- curl


### resources/settings.ini
remember to edit your settings.ini to reflect your settings.
